# ── InsightPulse — Netlify _redirects ────────────────────────────────────────
# This file is the production routing config for ana-pulse.netlify.app
#
# NOTE: netlify.toml takes precedence over this file for redirect rules.
# This file acts as a fallback and ensures SPA routing works even without
# netlify.toml being processed (e.g. in some edge cases).

# Proxy /api/* → Render backend (transparent — browser stays on ana-pulse.netlify.app)
/api/*  https://insightpulse-ja7r.onrender.com/api/:splat  200

# SPA fallback — all unmatched paths serve index.html (React Router handles routing)
/*      /index.html     200
